main event: A bright white object with flashes of red and green was observed in the sky over Kansas City, Missouri on August 11, 1965.
interesting points: The object appeared to stay in one place and was estimated to be at an altitude of 20,000 to 30,000 feet.
The object exhibited a brightness and flashing colors.
The object moved in a clockwise circular pattern from left to right.
The witness could not conclusively identify the object.
sighted object: a bright white object with flashing red and green lights
